41 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
NIBBLES AND BITS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
Compiled by Kenneth Williams 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Clarinetist Hakan G. Rosengren, 27, of San Clemente has been awarded a $12,000 
Solo Recitalist Fellowship from the National Endowment for the Arts. Rosengren 
will use the fellowship for a series of recitals in the Midwest during 
1991-1993. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA121490-0151 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 322403 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
December 14, 1990, Friday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
